{"id":151644,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/一年走遍世界记录全夜空照片/","date":"2011-05-11T05:00:37Z","modified":"2011-05-11T05:00:37Z","title":"一年走遍世界记录全夜空照片","content":"<p>摄影师Nick Risinger历时一年，旅行60，000英里，其中空中为45,000英里，陆地15,000英里，他利用一架机器人照相机和六个风冷照相机，每个都配备了镜头和滤镜，在一张照片里捕捉下整个夜空的图像。最后使用了37,440幅照片，耗时多月，合成出分辨率为5 Gigapixel的全球巡天照片。 Risinger称，光污染使得真正的夜空越来越难得一见。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14b6c193/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E8%B5%B0%E9%81%8D%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%85%A8%E5%A4%9C%E7%A9%BA%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F10%2F0622211%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E8%B5%B0%E9%81%8D%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%85%A8%E5%A4%9C%E7%A9%BA%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F10%2F0622211%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091839876/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14b6c193/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091839876/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14b6c193/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=bdhBefFpbcQ:hPvopOZq3XU:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=bdhBefFpbcQ:hPvopOZq3XU:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com